values.init-script:
echo "Starting up..."
invoke /rom/drv/aws/clone /boot/cfg/aws-creds /n/aws
invoke /rom/bin/ray-ssh /rom/bin/ray /n/ray-ssh
invoke /n/aws/sqs/receive-message /boot/cfg/aws-github-queue /tmp/message
: cat /tmp/message/body
echo "Done booting service"
